ticle/4728753-sangamo-fabry-disease-fene-therapy-moves-forward-positive-fda-development\">Seeking Alpha article</a> entitled \u201c<strong>Sangamo: Fabry Disease Gene Therapy Moves Forward With Positive FDA Regulatory Development.</strong></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2189638512/image_2189638512.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745407-sangamo-pipeline-expansion-via-partnership-and-internal-st-503-development", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 22:48:01"}, {"id": "4745406", "title": "GPIQ: Dynamic Options ETF With Monthly Distributions", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/10168515/image_10168515.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"MAN HOLDING MONEY WITH PIG MASK ON\" data-id=\"10168515\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1265px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/10168515/image_10168515.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/10168515/image_10168515.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/10168515/image_10168515.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/10168515/image_10168515.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/10168515/image_10168515.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/10168515/image_10168515.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/10168515/image_10168515.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/10168515/image_10168515.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Tim Platt/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Overview</h2> <p>There has been an abundance of new income-focused funds hitting the public markets, and they all vary in strategy, holdings, and risk profile. I've been on the hunt for some of the best quality holdings out there</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/10168515/image_10168515.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745406-gpiq-dynamic-options-etf-with-monthly-distributions", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 22:40:30"}, {"id": "4745403", "title": "Applied Materials In 2025: Cloudy With A Chance Of Windfalls", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468266081/image_1468266081.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Silicon Wafer during Photolithography Process. Shot of Lithography Process that allows to Create Complex Patterns on a Wafer during Semiconductor and Computer Chip Production at Fab or Foundry.\" data-id=\"1468266081\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468266081/image_1468266081.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468266081/image_1468266081.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468266081/image_1468266081.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468266081/image_1468266081.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468266081/image_1468266081.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468266081/image_1468266081.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468266081/image_1468266081.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468266081/image_1468266081.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">SweetBunFactory</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>Applied Materials (NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AMAT\" class=\"ticker-link\">AMAT</a>), the maker of semiconductor WFE, or Wafer Fabrication Equipment, has experienced a phenomenal few years where fabrication companies doubled down on purchasing more fabrication equipment to cope with the elevated demand for chips being</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468266081/image_1468266081.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745403-applied-materials-stock-in-2025-cloudy-with-chance-of-windfalls", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 22:36:20"}, {"id": "4745400", "title": "LTC Properties: Steady Growth Set To Continue In 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1454987355/image_1454987355.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Model house on calculator with stack of coins money on natural green background, Calculating interest payments and Property tax concept\" data-id=\"1454987355\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1454987355/image_1454987355.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1454987355/image_1454987355.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1454987355/image_1454987355.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080